              <span id="reviewTextContainer1945287447" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16539417536996306022">A 2003 Newbery Medal winner that is set in fourteenth-century England and is about an orphaned who is falsely accused of several crimes. This is first book in a trilogy about Crispin. Avi is a skillful storyteller and does a great job at capturing this time period. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


